<h1>Word Puzzle</h1>

<p>Create a word puzzle for someone to solve! Enter a word or phrase and all vowels will be replaced with dashes.</p>

<form action='/detector' method='get'>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="word">Enter word(s)</label>
    <input id="word" name="word" class="form-control" type="text">
  </div>
  <br>
  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info">Create word puzzle!</button>
  <p></p>
</form>
